item.title: Stratospheric Sessions 012
item.description:
After quite a hiatus, here is the latest Stratospheric Sessions episode featuring 90 minutes of some of the latest tunes in progressive, techno, and trance. Enjoy!
..::TRACKLIST::..
1. Kelevra - Naden 2. Falling [Commited to Sparkle Motion] (CLMD Remix) - Discopolis 3. Under a Sea of Birds (Andrew Whitfield Edit) - Joint Operation Centre 4. Tears of Tender - Ferhat Albayrak 5. Natural Touches - Kay-D 6. Player One (Gai Barone Remix) - Danilo Ercole 7. Immersion - Omnia 8. Rise Again (Omnia Remix) - Ronski Speed feat. Lucy Saunders 9. Trickster - Grube & Hovsepian 10. Dinodrums - Estiva 11. Panama (Mac & Monday Remix) - Substate 12. Inbound - Simon Bostock 13. Human - Ferrin & Morris 14. Hawaii (MilamDo pres. Harmonic Rush Remix) - Robien M 15. The Ultimate Destination - A.R.D.I. 16. Full Stop - Will Rees & Sam Jones

item.description: Here is my unedited opening DJ set recorded live from LMD's Grand Opening event feat. Roger Shah at the Belasco Ballroom. It was extremely exciting to have been the 1st DJ to kick off what I know will be a successful new chapter in LMD history. Hope you enjoy! ..::TRACKLIST::.. 1. Singapore Sling - Relaunch 6. Skeksis - Alan Fitzpatrick 7. Black Star - Filterheadz 8. Arctic Ice Fields - Silicon Syndicate 9. Rorschach - Jeremy Olander 10. Signals (Solid Stone Remix) - Sensitive5 & Gordey Tsukanov 11. Club Stalkin (Basil O'Glue Remix) - Tucandeo 12. Love Stimulation (Glenn Morrison & Bruce Aisher Remix) - Humate 13. Devotion (Aladiah Remix) - Liquid Soul 14. Suspense (Basil O'Glue Remix) - Relaunch 15. Crack Of Dawn (Trance Edit) - Relaunch 16. Relentless - Timewave 17. Hale Bopp (Timewave Remix) - JS16 & Orkidea

item.title: Stratospheric Sessions 011
item.description: After a 4 month hiatus, Stratospheric Sessions is back!! To make up for the lost time, I've decided to make this episode 1.5 hours versus the standard 1 hour show simply because there were too many good tunes to choose from and I simply couldn't decide which ones to cut out so I just included them all! Hope you enjoy!! ..:: TRACKLIST ::.. 1. The Longest Haul (Robert Nickson's Rnx Remix) - Zach Roth 2. Stingray (Styller Remix) - Matthew Peterson 3. Close Your Eyes (Basil O'Glue) - Purple Stories 4. Must Be The Love (Shogun Remix) - BT & Arty feat. Nadia Ali 5. The Absolute Relativity - Airwave & John 00 Fleming 6. Skeksis - Alan Fitzpatrick 7. Black Star - Filterhedz 8. Class War - Full Tilt 9. Greece - Protonica 10. Seretonin Overdose (Protonica Remix) - Ave Venture & Rocky 11. The Source (Suduaya Remix) - Ovnimoon 12. One Heart - (Lupin Remix) - Ovnimoon 13. Chase (Lupin Remix) - Zyce & Flegma 14. Come Together - Paul Oakenfold 15. Somnium - Trance Arts & Colin James 16. Airport - Photographer 17. Us (Estigma Bootleg) - Simon Patterson

item.title: Stratospheric Sessions 010
item.description: Welcome back for another episode of Stratospheric Sessions!! Tune in for this hour long mix of only the most pulsating, hypnotizing, body warping forms of trance around! For this episode, things get kicked off with some dark progressive tunes and from there go sweeping into some seriously twisted body rocking psy before capping it all off with some uplifting 140bpm trance! Tracklist can be seen below... ..::TRACKLIST::.. 1. Club Stalkin' (Basil O'Glue Remix) - Tucandeo 2. The Machine - Juventa & Johnny Yono 3. Airglow (Basil O'Glue Remix) - Raneem 4. The 10th Life (Artifact 303 Remix) - John 00 Fleming 5. Fight The Darkness (Ovnimoon Remix) - John 00 Fleming feat. Sascha Cooper 6. The Lost Tribe - Impact vs. Static Movement 7. Energy Flow - Sonic Entity feat. Nerso 8. Darker Shades of Black (Liquid Soul Remix) - Will Atkinson pres. Darkboy 9. Curveball - Chris Metcalfe 10. Dae Yor - Paul Van Dyk feat. Ummet Ozcan 11. Alchemy - Darren Porter

item.title: Stratospheric Sessions 009
item.description: Welcome back for another episode of Stratospheric Sessions!! I've switched things up a bit for this episode as I've done a completely 100% progressive-psy/psy-trance episode. I'm really excited about this and hope you guys enjoy it as much as I did mixing it! So without further delay, welcome to the wonderfully wicked world of psy! ..::TRACKLIST::.. 1. Out of Nowhere (Andrew Whitfield Edit) - Timewave 2. Super Sonic (Relaunch Remix) - Timewave 3. Year 2008 (Matteo Monero Remix) - Suffused 4. 8 Gig - Omair Mirza 5. Torn Melodies - Gaudium 6. Atlantic Spirit - Static Movement vs. Impact 7. Euphoria - Lyctum 8. Spirit World - Copycat 9. Greece 2000 - Lyctum 10. Shoreline - Nick Sentience 11. Think Differently (Micky Noise Remix) - DNA 12. Ark - John 00 Fleming & The Digital Blonde
